f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b5e9b2da2a11042fe7a023ced685cebf30be489b","tid":1630683,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=6bbf1a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n民調將於10月11日中午12時結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crPJOtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrPJOtZ.jpg&h=712eed78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f60ebc335678d3ca43bd4d33e60f823c7d97a6ff","tid":1630683,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacf7f4718164c54d8fb7ad38b7be8e06cfb5bf5","tid":1630683,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"出九龍方向定咩"}]}